item.title: 【Albums (lossy)】MP3 - Kristine Elezaj - No Questions Remain (2010 Version) (320 KBP/s)
item.description:
​

No Questions Remain is the debut (and as of now, only) album by Albanian-born singer Kristine Elezaj. It was released in October 2010 through ZAJ Recordings.

In recent years, a truncated version of No Questions Remain replaced the original 17-track release on streaming music apps. No explanation has been given as to why.

1. Siren Assassin
2. Kidnap the DJ
3. Let You Know
4. Warpath
5. Momentum
6. Barb Wire (feat. P-Dub)
7. Light Years
8. Rockstar
9. Do or Die
10. Always
11. Boy Toy
12. Souvenirs
13. Living Room
14. Always (Dance Remix)
15. Let You Know (Smashmode Remix)
